title: Good size, durable, great locket
text:
My boyfriend and I both bought one of these lockets. We love the size, pattern, and functionality — it was really exactly what we wanted! We’ve had them for over a year now and they’re still great.

A few points for consideration: it comes on a very small, thin chain. Fine for me (and it hasn’t broken yet), but we transferred my boy’s locket to a thicker and longer chain that he preferred.
Additionally, because the front of the locket has holes between the pattern, you have to be careful not to get the locket dirty. I’ve dunked mine in tea and ice cream by accident, and it’s a bit of a pain to clean (plus the picture inside came out a little wonky). However, I love that it’s an open pattern, so I forgive it.
